text: Jakub Marek (born June 22, 1991) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for EHC Waldkraiburg of the Bayernliga. Marek made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with Motor České Budějovice during the 2011-12 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Motor České Budějovice players Category:Stadion Hradec Králové players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards
